text: Asa John Lawrey Lees (1931 – 8 January 2008) was an Australian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1956 Summer Olympics.John Lees' obituary ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Australian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Australia Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
